	<div style="text-align:right;">
		KRUGER, Helington Castro<sup>1</sup>; FONTÃO, Flávia Noemy Gasparini Kiatake<sup>2</sup>; CLAUDINO, Marcela<sup>3</sup>; LOCKS, Bruna Jussara Constantino<sup>4</sup>; DITZEL, Alessandra Soares<sup>5</sup>; ALANIS, Luciana Reis Azevedo<sup>6</sup>		<BR>
